Transit Route Recs¶

Plot the transit route's line geom.

Brainstorm¶

Filter to intersecting SHN route within a district if:

  • average route speed is below 12 mph AND
  • 10%+ of its trips are competitive against a car traveling the same path (competitive is 1.5x...so bus can take 50% more time)
    • Move away from 2x threshold to be a bit more aggressive to select the ones that are really uncompetitive
    • Also use a certain percentage more for bus, rather than 20 min, 30 min, 40 min cut-offs because that requires us to factor in how long the overall route is (route_group)
    • 10%+ trips competitive to show that there's already some that are competitive against car, can do better...selecting 0% trips competitive gets circulator type routes
  • Get speedmaps for these set of routes for more detailed info?
